BASIC DROP COOKIES
1 1/4 c flour			1/2 c sugar
1/2 tsp baking soda		1/4 c packed brown sugar
1/2 tsp salt			1 egg	
1/4 c butter or margarine	1 tsp vanilla
1/4 c shortening

Combine flour, baking soda, and salt.   Beat butter and shortening for
30 seconds.  Add sugars and beat until fluffy.  Add egg and vanilla,
beating well.  Beat in dry ingredients.  Drop by teaspoons onto
greased cookie sheet.  Bake at 375 for 8 to 10 minutes.  Cool on a
wire rack.


